===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|dewk}}
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|abductiō||robbing; abduction}}, from {{m|la|abdūcō||take or lead away}}, from {{m|la|ab||away}} + {{m|la|dūcō||to lead}}<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=2}}</ref>.
* {{sense|physiology}} From {{etyl|fr|en}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|abductus}}.
* Compare French {{m|fr|abduction}}.

